descriptor.long_desc:
PACK CONTENT: This pack contains 15 pieces of Tata Simply Better plant-based Chicken Nuggets
TASTES JUST LIKE CHICKEN: Enjoy chicken-like texture, flavour, crunch, and juiciness. Try it to believe it!
RICH IN PROTEIN: These plant-based chicken nuggets are rich in protein with 12.2 g of protein per 100 g
TRANS FAT-FREE: It is trans-fat-free, making it a great choice
Packed with nutritional goodness and chicken-like taste – this product is free from added preservatives, and added colours

FREE FROM ANTIBIOTICS & HARMFUL HORMONES: Since it is plant based, it has no antibiotics and harmful hormones
ALSO TRY: Plant-Based Chicken Burger Patty, Plant-Based Chicken Awadhi Seekh Kebab, Plant-Based Chicken Spicy Fingers that all taste just like chicken
